properties.name: 東の海: Mare Orientale
properties.detail: One of the lunar seas located on the western edge of the moon's near side.

properties.name: 嵐の大洋: Oceanus Procellarum
properties.detail: The largest sea on the moon. Luna 9 and Surveyor 1 landed here. In the western part of the Ocean of Storms, the world's first hole leading underground was discovered.

properties.name: ラインホルト: Reinhold
properties.detail: Located to the south-southwest of Copernicus. Surrounding it are craters like Reinhold B and Reinhold C.

properties.name: コペルニクス: Copernicus
properties.detail: A relatively new crater that formed 800 million years ago. Infrared measurements indicate it's made from stones containing magnesium and iron.

properties.name: 晴れの海: Mare Serenitatis
properties.detail: One of the lunar seas located to the east of the Sea of Rains, covered with basalt.

properties.name: 雨の海: Mare Imbrium
properties.detail: The second-largest lunar sea after the Ocean of Storms.

properties.name: ティコ: Tycho
properties.detail: A new crater formed 180 million years ago. Due to the materials covering it, its temperature drops slower than its surroundings.

properties.name: プラトー: Plato
properties.detail: A crater located in the northern part. Within this crater, there are four more craters with a diameter of 2 kilometers each.

properties.name: スミス海: Mare Smythii
properties.detail: One of the lunar seas located near the moon's equator.

properties.name: アリストテレス: Aristoteles
properties.detail: Located in the northern part of the moon. The surface of Aristotle has a rough texture.

properties.name: エウドクソス: Eudoxus
properties.detail: If the air currents aren't stable, clear images can't be taken.

properties.name: 静かの海: Mare Tranquillitatis
properties.detail: The location where Apollo 11's lander touched down. There's a crater named after the three astronauts of Apollo 11.

properties.name: アポロ11号着陸地点: Apollo 11 landing site
properties.detail: Landed on July 20, 1969, north of the Sea of Tranquility's Lamont.

properties.name: アームストロング: Armstrong
properties.detail: Named in honor of Apollo 11's commander, Neil Armstrong.

properties.name: コリンズ: Collins
properties.detail: Named in honor of Apollo 11's Michael Collins.

properties.name: オルドリン: Aldrin
properties.detail: Named in honor of Apollo 11's crew member, Buzz Aldrin.
